{"tid":2389147,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"唔知香港遲啲會唔會有一陣簡體字潮流？","createTime":"2021-01-31T16:04:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-01T07:58:09.000Z","uid":201464,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1e1448f88f06e1616034dd914b6f011746105d8c","tid":2389147,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T16:04:35.000Z","msg":"台灣已經搶先一步<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dcard.tw/f/girl/p/235251075?region=HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dcard.tw%2Ff%2Fgirl%2Fp%2F235251075%3Fregion%3DHK&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1G4gDU6S0x1vJ5b5MQMl6fZo%3D&h=7ebb4e06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.dcard.tw/f/girl/p/235251075?region=HK</a><br />\n<blockquote>現在國中生用簡體字是最新潮流？<br />\n用小紅書的人多嗎～～～～<br />\n<br />\n看到朋友分享這貼文</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.dcard.tw/BiiPXZ5h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.dcard.tw%2FBiiPXZ5h.jpg&h=a6089f81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://imgur.dcard.tw/ze9FesEh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.dcard.tw%2Fze9FesEh.jpg&h=c569f143&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://imgur.dcard.tw/VStVs1uh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.dcard.tw%2FVStVs1uh.jpg&h=5fc96cd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://imgur.dcard.tw/v0t5nf2h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.dcard.tw%2Fv0t5nf2h.jpg&h=fc253c72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://imgur.dcard.tw/ajWMieRh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.dcard.tw%2FajWMieRh.jpg&h=64e74234&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"de64da97172e8cd356881b0539178ca27d3fd2c4","tid":2389147,"uid":201464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T16:05:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>現在國高中生<br />\n覺得用簡體字是種潮流？<br />\n<br />\n朋友有個念高中的表妹<br />\n打字都用簡體字<br />\n說話也很多中國用語<br />\n身邊沒有年紀比較小的親戚<br />\n所以不太知道實際狀況<br />\n當初聽到覺得扯、怎麼可能啊<br />\n<br />\n看到這個貼文之後<br />\n發現好像真的有這個現象？<br />\n<br />\n這個現在應該不只是小紅書<br />\n還有很多遊戲影片、實況主、陸劇陸綜等等</blockquote>"},{"pid":"8c1b2400479ceacd893e6857c63039be1d366273","tid":2389147,"uid":201464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T16:06:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>給一些不知道什麼是小紅書的人：<br />\n<br />\n「小紅書就像中國的 instagram 一般，圖像為主，能滿足無法使用 IG 的少男少女們，在上面分享照片累積點閱，它不像抖音那樣要充滿快速娛樂性質，反而多了點【慢質感】，且中國現在經濟能力高，用戶紛紛在上面分享去了哪裡玩、買了什麼精品⋯令人羨慕仿效。」（電商人妻， 2019）<br />\n<br />\nＱＱＱＱ<br />\n還有網友說：「現在已經一堆國高中生的IG自介都直接放簡體字了」<br />\n<br />\n這是所謂的世代隔閡嗎XDD<br />\n台灣的下一代要被統了ㄇ<br />\n<br />\n哭啊</blockquote>"},{"pid":"c33d4024391e59a78ccba4e439a2d15ab493b820","tid":2389147,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T16:07:58.000Z","msg":"台灣佬成日講裝b"},{"pid":"92183e22aa5c71676fedaf7ac6e4897c8f4cf510","tid":2389147,"uid":108016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T16:09:54.000Z","msg":"遲早<br />\n啲人都開始走"},{"pid":"6545cf7f2399be46b78de09af3f135935ac1a46d","tid":2389147,"uid":210161,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T16:13:08.000Z","msg":"香港以前考AL寫文 大把人寫簡體啦"},{"pid":"00ba0f16b89d8d7b991ea3c9a865a4e1190030c9","tid":2389147,"uid":201464,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"6545cf7f2399be46b78de09af3f135935ac1a46d","tid":2389147,"uid":210161,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T16:13:08.000Z","msg":"香港以前考AL寫文 大把人寫簡體啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T18:12:14.000Z","msg":"點同？<br />\n係寫唔切先寫定係潮流？"},{"pid":"9494e674d9f654b1fc99d34a8fdabe4a5eaabd83","tid":2389147,"uid":92479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T18:54:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1a9ef9ba3b965c9a103fd549e019f7fa753ebce","tid":2389147,"uid":54125,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T18:57:07.000Z","msg":"19年以前有過<